description: The great inner wall of the keep is featureless, except for a reinforced vaalorn gate, which is guarded by quite a number of Ta'Vaalorian militia stationed on either side of the gate.  Occasionally the militia guards inspect the papers of special couriers entering the inner keep and keep a stern eye on everyone going in or out.

title: [Guardian Keep, Postern Gate]
